** RECURSION : IF U WANT TO PRINT NO FROM 1 TO N USING RECURSION THEN TAKE 1 IN FUN CALL FIRST **

class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        fun(1);
    }
    static void fun(int n)
    {
        if(n==4)
        {
            return;
        }
        System.out.print(n+" "); // Print before the recursive call
        fun(n+1);
    }
}

op : 1 2 3